{"id": 2596, "genre": 1001, "title": "在国内办事填表格，你都有哪些无从下笔的迷思？", "description": "政治面貌填国字脸行不行？（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA Images）", "record_count": 2837, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181030112340a9gQFfvCuTcEpRqm.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-12-24T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 318466, "content": "政治面貌，一大把年纪了还在填“团员”", "image": null, "praise_count": 704, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498034}, {"id": 318467, "content": "ZZCF", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749248}, {"id": 318469, "content": "没事28自动退团吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 66, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 431020}, {"id": 318471, "content": "婚姻状况写单身不行吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 96, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341628}, {"id": 318472, "content": "结婚登记的时候，填职业硬是没找到互联网相关的行业，勉强勾了个新闻出版、文化工作者", "image": null, "praise_count": 79, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324907}, {"id": 318986, "content": "个人特长:没有特长", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541929}, {"id": 318476, "content": "家庭出身", "image": null, "praise_count": 140, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009175}, {"id": 318477, "content": "看到过一个党员同学，政治面貌写的是“贫农”，当时就惊呆了", "image": null, "praise_count": 234, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278872}, {"id": 318478, "content": "爸妈年龄工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 161, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011810}, {"id": 318479, "content": "家庭出身", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1476492}, {"id": 318480, "content": "配偶的简历也要填😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540067}, {"id": 318482, "content": "作为柜员一名，重要联系人的身份证号真是难为了好多人", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540826}, {"id": 318483, "content": "民族", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327272}, {"id": 318485, "content": "除了姓名性别身份证号以外，很多都难以下笔，奇葩到不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 113, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493981}, {"id": 318486, "content": "健康状况永远良好", "image": null, "praise_count": 89, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377387}, {"id": 318489, "content": "父母  单位  职务", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926806}, {"id": 318492, "content": "收入情况🙄", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1255413}, {"id": 318494, "content": "个人特长，获得奖项", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1322032}, {"id": 318495, "content": "填自我评价一直是:自我感觉良好，无不良嗜好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1536736}, {"id": 318500, "content": "自从把特长变成专业以后，特长就不知道填什么。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 65, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358680}, {"id": 318501, "content": "我都不知道我政治面貌是啥，入团也是当初班主任为了指标强行帮我入的", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251294}, {"id": 318503, "content": "初中的时候老师要求填表，特长实在不知道怎么写。我就写了个“一秒钟可以编出个句子”🤣", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540051}, {"id": 318506, "content": "身高、体重", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429934}, {"id": 318507, "content": "家庭成员，不知道该不该把爷爷奶奶辈还有叔叔阿姨写进去", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366841}, {"id": 319276, "content": "填写父母的个人信息？？？\r\n是我入职还是父母入职！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 318509, "content": "本人成分…我觉得本人可能就是肉和水😅", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1449610}, {"id": 318510, "content": "面试填表格居然看到“喝什么牌子酒”、“抽什么牌子香烟”😂我就写下了“富贵不饮酒”、“自强不吸烟”☺", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340666}, {"id": 318511, "content": "经常出现的无不良嗜好的“不良嗜好”是否包括吸烟，如果包括那么差不多一半男人不合格了。\n不良嗜好是否包括看黄片，如果包括的话男人整体都不合格了。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340666}, {"id": 318512, "content": "宗教信仰", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 771335}, {"id": 318513, "content": "城镇户口还是农村户口……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540109}, {"id": 318514, "content": "有没有女朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473721}, {"id": 318515, "content": "28岁自动退团哦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540190}, {"id": 318517, "content": "让填特长和爱好的时候，到底多特长算特长？有多爱好算爱好？写我爱打游戏行吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147717}, {"id": 318776, "content": "成分 🤣", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218908}, {"id": 319035, "content": "\n获得奖项", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1542264}, {"id": 318529, "content": "群众", "image": "img/option/option/201812241640387ijVJ8FbNWyRUreY.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540270}, {"id": 319043, "content": "你的优点是什么？\r\n你的缺点是什么？\r\n你为什么离职？\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 318532, "content": "太可怜了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1328523}, {"id": 318788, "content": "个人成分：水", "image": "img/option/option/20181225200427oCF5nQRI3csf1Z9A", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1138758}, {"id": 318789, "content": "个人成分：水", "image": "img/option/option/20181225200513JXTFEQturx8Nnlf3", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1138758}, {"id": 318790, "content": "个人成分：水", "image": "img/option/option/2018122520063027f3tZIXHkL5yxzJ", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1138758}, {"id": 318535, "content": "职位，职称，岗位…分不清", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 621083}, {"id": 318536, "content": "“从事行业”\n不知道是哪个年代的分类规则，经常找不到相对应的", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796009}, {"id": 319316, "content": "本人成分，碳基生物", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1394514}, {"id": 318550, "content": "父母的单位", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1127762}, {"id": 318551, "content": "特长，总觉得无从下笔。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493233}, {"id": 318552, "content": "特长，最纠结的一个", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511904}, {"id": 319064, "content": "是否单身", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1542400}, {"id": 318553, "content": "爸爸妈妈爷爷奶奶外公外婆的年薪...", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540373}, {"id": 318557, "content": "个人爱好真的迷啊……感觉什么算是爱好？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1295118}]}